Requires-Dist: Trac

This plugin allows you to view your trac.log logfile without shell access, just via the Web-UI Admin interface. You can select to only display messages from a specified log level (e.g. only warnings), optionally including higher levels. Moreover, you may restrict the output to the latest N lines, and even filter for lines containing a specified string or even matching a regular expression.


